<body>
	<article id="bfebb424-4727-484a-bde0-32ed3e078464" class="page sans">
		<header>
			<div class="page-header-icon undefined"><img class="icon" src="https://www.notion.so/icons/cursor-click_red.svg" /></div>
			<h1 class="page-title">프론트엔드(FE)</h1>
			<p class="page-description" />
		</header>
		<div class="page-body">
			<p id="ef8557d1-3632-43cf-9678-0721f7f38f90" class="">
				A Frontend Developer is a type of web developer who specializes in creating the visual and interactive components of a website or
				web application.
			</p>
			<p id="66bd0772-1b07-45ec-a6af-ada2f59ccadf" class="">
				FE-Dev work on the client side of web development, meaning we focus on what the user sees and interacts with on the website or
				application.
			</p>
			<p id="ccc55643-001e-4f2b-bb62-3987c9fd56e3" class="" />
			<h2 id="0d8c6a4d-62a8-4b92-8deb-0f7cde594c2d" class=""><mark class="highlight-pink">the key skills and knowledge</mark></h2>
			<ol type="1" id="086283a8-2af5-40e9-aa05-abf8f4e1859b" class="numbered-list" start="1">
				<li>
					Proficiency in <strong>HTML</strong>, <strong>CSS</strong>, and <strong>JavaScript </strong>- these are the foundational languages
					of web development and are essential for creating the
					<mark class="highlight-orange"><strong>user interface</strong></mark> and user experience of a website or web application.
				</li>
			</ol>
			<ol type="1" id="735f7c90-f63d-4198-8e9e-b99ba8197d80" class="numbered-list" start="2">
				<li>
					Familiarity with Frontend frameworks and libraries - Frontend Developers may use libraries and frameworks like <mark
						class="highlight-orange"><strong>React</strong></mark
					><mark class="highlight-orange">, </mark><mark class="highlight-orange"><strong>Vue.js</strong></mark><mark
						class="highlight-orange"
						>, or
					</mark><mark class="highlight-orange"><strong>Angular</strong></mark><strong />to streamline the development process and create
					more complex and dynamic user interfaces.
				</li>
			</ol>
			<ol type="1" id="356c76a4-fbb1-48d4-925d-fa1bdf3382dc" class="numbered-list" start="3">
				<li>
					<mark class="highlight-orange">Understanding of design principles and user experience (UX)</mark> - Frontend Developers work closely
					with UX designers and need to have an understanding of design principles to create visually appealing and intuitive user interfaces.
				</li>
			</ol>
			<ol type="1" id="84c07c13-7f14-4524-927b-b83ff68fb949" class="numbered-list" start="4">
				<li>
					Knowledge of web <mark class="highlight-orange">performance optimization</mark> - Frontend Developers need to ensure that their websites
					and applications load quickly and perform well on different devices and platforms.
				</li>
			</ol>
			<ol type="1" id="b8b69c87-bcf7-4483-8854-7b1918c415b9" class="numbered-list" start="5">
				<li>
					Experience with version <mark class="highlight-orange">control and collaboration tools</mark> - Frontend Developers often work in teams
					and need to be comfortable with using version control tools like Git and collaborating on projects using tools like GitHub or Bitbucket.
				</li>
			</ol>
			<ol type="1" id="c557f077-88a4-46a9-9e54-c7956b04a6c0" class="numbered-list" start="6">
				<li>
					<mark class="highlight-orange">Understanding of web accessibility</mark> - Frontend Developers need to ensure that their websites and
					applications are accessible to all users, including those with disabilities.
				</li>
			</ol>
			<h2 id="3e8ded61-0bbf-4652-ac40-d2231f8fe9e5" class=""><mark class="highlight-pink">Overall</mark></h2>
			<p id="dc18db05-4cb2-43f9-b827-c5f451593efb" class="">
				Frontend Developers play a crucial role in creating<strong /><mark class="highlight-orange"
					><strong>the user-facing aspects</strong></mark> of websites and web applications.
			</p>
			<p id="fe46a2d2-8b68-4b7e-9104-450b9022d10e" class="">
				They need to possess a wide range of technical and creative skills and stay up-to-date with the latest technologies and trends in
				web development
			</p>
			<p id="3d43fb8d-2e56-4e23-95f4-93c6a536be7d" class="">
				to create compelling and<mark class="highlight-orange"><strong> effective user interfaces.</strong></mark>
			</p>
